<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Voucher Template</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@300;400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            page-break-after: always;
            background-color: #f4f4f9;
        }
        .page {
            width: 303mm;
            height: 216mm;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            padding: 20mm;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .voucher {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            border: 2px solid #4a90e2;
            background-color: #fff;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 20mm;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .voucher-header {
            font-size: 36px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #4a90e2;
            margin-bottom: 10mm;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .voucher-content {
            font-size: 18px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 10mm;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        .voucher-footer {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #909090;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .qr-code {
            width: 50mm;
            height: 50mm;
            background-color: #f4f4f9;
            border: 1px dashed #ccc;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            margin-top: 10mm;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="page">
        <div class="voucher">
            <div class="voucher-header">QRSong Credit Voucher</div>
            <div class="voucher-content">
                <p>Congratulations! You've received a special QRSong credit voucher.</p>
                <p>Use this voucher to unlock exclusive music experiences.</p>
                <div class="qr-code">
                    <p>QR Code Here</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="voucher-footer">Valid until: [Expiration Date]</div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="page">
        <div class="voucher">
            <div class="voucher-content">
                <p>Terms and Conditions:</p>
                <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Integer nec odio. Praesent libero. Sed cursus ante dapibus diam.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
